{"title":"给乌兰诺娃——看巴蕾舞“小夜曲”后作","authors":["艾青"],"dates":[{"year":1952,"month":11,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给乌兰诺娃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——看巴蕾舞“小夜曲”后作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艾青"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像云一样柔软，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像风一样轻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比月光更明亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比夜更宁静——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人体在大空里游行；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是天上的仙女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却是人间的女神，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比梦更美，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比幻想更动人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——是劳动创造的结晶。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}